text: "The Carpal Tunnel of Love" is a 2007 single by Fall Out Boy. It was released in the United States on February 5, 2007, on the iTunes Store, and was not put out on a CD. The music video contains people from the television program Happy Tree Friends. ==Other websites== *Video Clip on YouTube Category:2007 songs Category:Fall Out Boy songs
